[09-May-21 05:42 PM] Hop Bot#1169

{Embed}
Commands for ROLE
**__list__**
Description: Gets a list of roles that can be modified by the user
Example: *>role list*
**__count__**
Description: Counts how many people have a certain role
Example: *>role count Admins*
**__add__**
Description: Add 1 or more roles to yourself
Example: *>role add C++ Java Linux*
**__remove__**
Description: Remove 1 or more roles from yourself
Example: *>role remove C++ Java Linux*

[29-May-21 08:13 PM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Economy Plugin
`!buy [name]`
Buy any item from the shop

`!daily`
Claim your daily coins. Claim on consecutive days to earn a streak bonus.

`!coins (optional member)`
Get the coins amount of anyone in the server

`!dice [amount]`
Throw two dice and try to get more points than your opponent to gain coins

`!economy-info`
Everything you need to know about the economy of this server

`!games`
Get more info about server's games

`!give-item [member] [name] [amount]`
Give an item from your inventory to a member

`!guess [amount]`
Guess the number between 1 and 100 to gain coins

`!items (optional member)`
List the items you bought from the shop

`!richest`
Get the richest players of the server

`!rps [amount] [sign]`
Play rock paper scissors and try to gain coins

`!roulette [amount]`
Play roulette and try to gain coins

`!shop (optional name)`
List items from the shop

`!use [name]`
Use an item from your inventory

`!work (optional action)`
Work for one hour and come back to claim your paycheck

[29-May-21 09:25 PM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Gamble up to 240 :existentialdread: for each game

**Dice**
`!dice <amount>`
Throw two dice and try to make more than your opponent to gain your bet. Make a double and win twice this amount. Make a double 6 and win three times this amount.
_gains: from x1 to x3 depending on your dice_

**Guess The Number**
`!guess <amount>`
Guess the random number between **1 and 100**, in 5 attempts to gain your bet. The less attempts you use, the more you gain (**x10** in one shot).
_gains: from x0.5 to x10 depending on the attempts_

**Roshambo (rock, paper, scissors)**
`!rps <amount> <sign>`
Win at rock paper scissors against your opponent to gain your bet
_gains: x1_

**Roulette**
`!roulette <amount>`
Survive to the roulette game to gain your bet. A 6 bullets :gun: is used, the more you replay, the more you gain (x4 if you survive the 5 shots). Answer `continue` to continue using the same :gun: and increase your gain... at your own risks
_gains: from x1 to x4 depending on the round you reach_

[29-May-21 09:29 PM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Economy Plugin
`!buy [name]`
Buy any item from the shop

`!daily`
Claim your daily coins. Claim on consecutive days to earn a streak bonus.

`!coins (optional member)`
Get the coins amount of anyone in the server

`!dice [amount]`
Throw two dice and try to get more points than your opponent to gain coins

`!economy-info`
Everything you need to know about the economy of this server

`!games`
Get more info about server's games

`!give-item [member] [name] [amount]`
Give an item from your inventory to a member

`!guess [amount]`
Guess the number between 1 and 100 to gain coins

`!items (optional member)`
List the items you bought from the shop

`!richest`
Get the richest players of the server

`!rps [amount] [sign]`
Play rock paper scissors and try to gain coins

`!roulette [amount]`
Play roulette and try to gain coins

`!shop (optional name)`
List items from the shop

`!use [name]`
Use an item from your inventory

`!work (optional action)`
Work for one hour and come back to claim your paycheck

[30-May-21 06:37 AM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Economy Plugin
`!buy [name]`
Buy any item from the shop

`!daily`
Claim your daily coins. Claim on consecutive days to earn a streak bonus.

`!coins (optional member)`
Get the coins amount of anyone in the server

`!dice [amount]`
Throw two dice and try to get more points than your opponent to gain coins

`!economy-info`
Everything you need to know about the economy of this server

`!games`
Get more info about server's games

`!give-item [member] [name] [amount]`
Give an item from your inventory to a member

`!guess [amount]`
Guess the number between 1 and 100 to gain coins

`!items (optional member)`
List the items you bought from the shop

`!richest`
Get the richest players of the server

`!rps [amount] [sign]`
Play rock paper scissors and try to gain coins

`!roulette [amount]`
Play roulette and try to gain coins

`!shop (optional name)`
List items from the shop

`!use [name]`
Use an item from your inventory

`!work (optional action)`
Work for one hour and come back to claim your paycheck

[30-May-21 09:35 AM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Economy Plugin
`!buy [name]`
Buy any item from the shop

`!daily`
Claim your daily coins. Claim on consecutive days to earn a streak bonus.

`!coins (optional member)`
Get the coins amount of anyone in the server

`!dice [amount]`
Throw two dice and try to get more points than your opponent to gain coins

`!economy-info`
Everything you need to know about the economy of this server

`!games`
Get more info about server's games

`!give-coins [member] [amount]`
Give coins to anyone in the server

`!give-item [member] [name] [amount]`
Give an item from your inventory to a member

`!guess [amount]`
Guess the number between 1 and 100 to gain coins

`!items (optional member)`
List the items you bought from the shop

`!remove-coins [member] [amount]`
Remove coins from anyone in the server

`!remove-item [member] [name] [amount]`
Remove an item from someone's inventory

`!richest`
Get the richest players of the server

`!rps [amount] [sign]`
Play rock paper scissors and try to gain coins

`!roulette [amount]`
Play roulette and try to gain coins

[30-May-21 09:35 AM] bag#6347
!games


[30-May-21 09:35 AM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Gamble up to 240 :existentialdread: for each game

**Dice**
`!dice <amount>`
Throw two dice and try to make more than your opponent to gain your bet. Make a double and win twice this amount. Make a double 6 and win three times this amount.
_gains: from x1 to x3 depending on your dice_

**Guess The Number**
`!guess <amount>`
Guess the random number between **1 and 100**, in 5 attempts to gain your bet. The less attempts you use, the more you gain (**x10** in one shot).
_gains: from x0.5 to x10 depending on the attempts_

**Roshambo (rock, paper, scissors)**
`!rps <amount> <sign>`
Win at rock paper scissors against your opponent to gain your bet
_gains: x1_

**Roulette**
`!roulette <amount>`
Survive to the roulette game to gain your bet. A 6 bullets :gun: is used, the more you replay, the more you gain (x4 if you survive the 5 shots). Answer `continue` to continue using the same :gun: and increase your gain... at your own risks
_gains: from x1 to x4 depending on the round you reach_

!games


[30-May-21 03:57 PM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Gamble up to 240 :existentialdread: for each game

**Dice**
`!dice <amount>`
Throw two dice and try to make more than your opponent to gain your bet. Make a double and win twice this amount. Make a double 6 and win three times this amount.
_gains: from x1 to x3 depending on your dice_

**Guess The Number**
`!guess <amount>`
Guess the random number between **1 and 100**, in 5 attempts to gain your bet. The less attempts you use, the more you gain (**x10** in one shot).
_gains: from x0.5 to x10 depending on the attempts_

**Roshambo (rock, paper, scissors)**
`!rps <amount> <sign>`
Win at rock paper scissors against your opponent to gain your bet
_gains: x1_

**Roulette**
`!roulette <amount>`
Survive to the roulette game to gain your bet. A 6 bullets :gun: is used, the more you replay, the more you gain (x4 if you survive the 5 shots). Answer `continue` to continue using the same :gun: and increase your gain... at your own risks
_gains: from x1 to x4 depending on the round you reach_

[30-May-21 04:02 PM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Economy Plugin
`!buy [name]`
Buy any item from the shop

`!daily`
Claim your daily coins. Claim on consecutive days to earn a streak bonus.

`!coins (optional member)`
Get the coins amount of anyone in the server

`!dice [amount]`
Throw two dice and try to get more points than your opponent to gain coins

`!economy-info`
Everything you need to know about the economy of this server

`!games`
Get more info about server's games

`!give-item [member] [name] [amount]`
Give an item from your inventory to a member

`!guess [amount]`
Guess the number between 1 and 100 to gain coins

`!items (optional member)`
List the items you bought from the shop

`!richest`
Get the richest players of the server

`!rps [amount] [sign]`
Play rock paper scissors and try to gain coins

`!roulette [amount]`
Play roulette and try to gain coins

`!shop (optional name)`
List items from the shop

`!use [name]`
Use an item from your inventory

`!work (optional action)`
Work for one hour and come back to claim your paycheck


[30-May-21 04:02 PM] Binkiklou#7592

[30-May-21 04:02 PM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Gamble up to 240 :existentialdread: for each game

**Dice**
`!dice <amount>`
Throw two dice and try to make more than your opponent to gain your bet. Make a double and win twice this amount. Make a double 6 and win three times this amount.
_gains: from x1 to x3 depending on your dice_

**Guess The Number**
`!guess <amount>`
Guess the random number between **1 and 100**, in 5 attempts to gain your bet. The less attempts you use, the more you gain (**x10** in one shot).
_gains: from x0.5 to x10 depending on the attempts_

**Roshambo (rock, paper, scissors)**
`!rps <amount> <sign>`
Win at rock paper scissors against your opponent to gain your bet
_gains: x1_

**Roulette**
`!roulette <amount>`
Survive to the roulette game to gain your bet. A 6 bullets :gun: is used, the more you replay, the more you gain (x4 if you survive the 5 shots). Answer `continue` to continue using the same :gun: and increase your gain... at your own risks
_gains: from x1 to x4 depending on the round you reach_

[30-May-21 05:14 PM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Economy Plugin
`!buy [name]`
Buy any item from the shop

`!daily`
Claim your daily coins. Claim on consecutive days to earn a streak bonus.

`!coins (optional member)`
Get the coins amount of anyone in the server

`!dice [amount]`
Throw two dice and try to get more points than your opponent to gain coins

`!economy-info`
Everything you need to know about the economy of this server

`!games`
Get more info about server's games

`!give-item [member] [name] [amount]`
Give an item from your inventory to a member

`!guess [amount]`
Guess the number between 1 and 100 to gain coins

`!items (optional member)`
List the items you bought from the shop

`!richest`
Get the richest players of the server

`!rps [amount] [sign]`
Play rock paper scissors and try to gain coins

`!roulette [amount]`
Play roulette and try to gain coins

`!shop (optional name)`
List items from the shop

`!use [name]`
Use an item from your inventory

`!work (optional action)`
Work for one hour and come back to claim your paycheck

[30-May-21 06:01 PM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Gamble up to 240 :existentialdread: for each game

**Dice**
`!dice <amount>`
Throw two dice and try to make more than your opponent to gain your bet. Make a double and win twice this amount. Make a double 6 and win three times this amount.
_gains: from x1 to x3 depending on your dice_

**Guess The Number**
`!guess <amount>`
Guess the random number between **1 and 100**, in 5 attempts to gain your bet. The less attempts you use, the more you gain (**x10** in one shot).
_gains: from x0.5 to x10 depending on the attempts_

**Roshambo (rock, paper, scissors)**
`!rps <amount> <sign>`
Win at rock paper scissors against your opponent to gain your bet
_gains: x1_

**Roulette**
`!roulette <amount>`
Survive to the roulette game to gain your bet. A 6 bullets :gun: is used, the more you replay, the more you gain (x4 if you survive the 5 shots). Answer `continue` to continue using the same :gun: and increase your gain... at your own risks
_gains: from x1 to x4 depending on the round you reach_

Commands
For help with a specific command, type `;help <command>`

  print('13 + 12 = 24,')
  print('therefore,')
  print('12 + 13 = 24')
  print('QED')```

Economy Plugin
`!shop (optional name)`
List items from the shop

`!spawn-item [member] [name] [amount]`
Spawn an item in someone's inventory

`!use [name]`
Use an item from your inventory

`!work (optional action)`
Work for one hour and come back to claim your paycheck

[30-May-21 10:02 PM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Gamble up to 240 :existentialdread: for each game

**Dice**
`!dice <amount>`
Throw two dice and try to make more than your opponent to gain your bet. Make a double and win twice this amount. Make a double 6 and win three times this amount.
_gains: from x1 to x3 depending on your dice_

**Guess The Number**
`!guess <amount>`
Guess the random number between **1 and 100**, in 5 attempts to gain your bet. The less attempts you use, the more you gain (**x10** in one shot).
_gains: from x0.5 to x10 depending on the attempts_

**Roshambo (rock, paper, scissors)**
`!rps <amount> <sign>`
Win at rock paper scissors against your opponent to gain your bet
_gains: x1_

**Roulette**
`!roulette <amount>`
Survive to the roulette game to gain your bet. A 6 bullets :gun: is used, the more you replay, the more you gain (x4 if you survive the 5 shots). Answer `continue` to continue using the same :gun: and increase your gain... at your own risks
_gains: from x1 to x4 depending on the round you reach_

[30-May-21 11:21 PM] Hop Bot#1169

{Embed}
Commands for ROLE
**__list__**
Description: Gets a list of roles that can be modified by the user
Example: *>role list*
**__count__**
Description: Counts how many people have a certain role
Example: *>role count Admins*
**__add__**
Description: Add 1 or more roles to yourself
Example: *>role add C++ Java Linux*
**__remove__**
Description: Remove 1 or more roles from yourself
Example: *>role remove C++ Java Linux*

{Embed}
Economy Plugin
`!buy [name]`
Buy any item from the shop

`!daily`
Claim your daily coins. Claim on consecutive days to earn a streak bonus.

`!coins (optional member)`
Get the coins amount of anyone in the server

`!dice [amount]`
Throw two dice and try to get more points than your opponent to gain coins

`!economy-info`
Everything you need to know about the economy of this server

`!games`
Get more info about server's games

`!give-coins [member] [amount]`
Give coins to anyone in the server

`!give-item [member] [name] [amount]`
Give an item from your inventory to a member

`!guess [amount]`
Guess the number between 1 and 100 to gain coins

`!items (optional member)`
List the items you bought from the shop

`!remove-coins [member] [amount]`
Remove coins from anyone in the server

`!remove-item [member] [name] [amount]`
Remove an item from someone's inventory

`!richest`
Get the richest players of the server

`!rps [amount] [sign]`
Play rock paper scissors and try to gain coins

`!roulette [amount]`
Play roulette and try to gain coins

[31-May-21 12:33 AM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Gamble up to 240 :existentialdread: for each game

**Dice**
`!dice <amount>`
Throw two dice and try to make more than your opponent to gain your bet. Make a double and win twice this amount. Make a double 6 and win three times this amount.
_gains: from x1 to x3 depending on your dice_

**Guess The Number**
`!guess <amount>`
Guess the random number between **1 and 100**, in 5 attempts to gain your bet. The less attempts you use, the more you gain (**x10** in one shot).
_gains: from x0.5 to x10 depending on the attempts_

**Roshambo (rock, paper, scissors)**
`!rps <amount> <sign>`
Win at rock paper scissors against your opponent to gain your bet
_gains: x1_

**Roulette**
`!roulette <amount>`
Survive to the roulette game to gain your bet. A 6 bullets :gun: is used, the more you replay, the more you gain (x4 if you survive the 5 shots). Answer `continue` to continue using the same :gun: and increase your gain... at your own risks
_gains: from x1 to x4 depending on the round you reach_

[31-May-21 12:35 AM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Economy Plugin
`!buy [name]`
Buy any item from the shop

`!daily`
Claim your daily coins. Claim on consecutive days to earn a streak bonus.

`!coins (optional member)`
Get the coins amount of anyone in the server

`!dice [amount]`
Throw two dice and try to get more points than your opponent to gain coins

`!economy-info`
Everything you need to know about the economy of this server

`!games`
Get more info about server's games

`!give-item [member] [name] [amount]`
Give an item from your inventory to a member

`!guess [amount]`
Guess the number between 1 and 100 to gain coins

`!items (optional member)`
List the items you bought from the shop

`!richest`
Get the richest players of the server

`!rps [amount] [sign]`
Play rock paper scissors and try to gain coins

`!roulette [amount]`
Play roulette and try to gain coins

`!shop (optional name)`
List items from the shop

`!use [name]`
Use an item from your inventory

`!work (optional action)`
Work for one hour and come back to claim your paycheck

[31-May-21 02:44 PM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Economy Plugin
`!buy [name]`
Buy any item from the shop

`!daily`
Claim your daily coins. Claim on consecutive days to earn a streak bonus.

`!coins (optional member)`
Get the coins amount of anyone in the server

`!dice [amount]`
Throw two dice and try to get more points than your opponent to gain coins

`!economy-info`
Everything you need to know about the economy of this server

`!games`
Get more info about server's games

`!give-item [member] [name] [amount]`
Give an item from your inventory to a member

`!guess [amount]`
Guess the number between 1 and 100 to gain coins

`!items (optional member)`
List the items you bought from the shop

`!richest`
Get the richest players of the server

`!rps [amount] [sign]`
Play rock paper scissors and try to gain coins

`!roulette [amount]`
Play roulette and try to gain coins

`!shop (optional name)`
List items from the shop

`!use [name]`
Use an item from your inventory

`!work (optional action)`
Work for one hour and come back to claim your paycheck

!games


[31-May-21 08:45 PM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Gamble up to 240 :existentialdread: for each game

**Dice**
`!dice <amount>`
Throw two dice and try to make more than your opponent to gain your bet. Make a double and win twice this amount. Make a double 6 and win three times this amount.
_gains: from x1 to x3 depending on your dice_

**Guess The Number**
`!guess <amount>`
Guess the random number between **1 and 100**, in 5 attempts to gain your bet. The less attempts you use, the more you gain (**x10** in one shot).
_gains: from x0.5 to x10 depending on the attempts_

**Roshambo (rock, paper, scissors)**
`!rps <amount> <sign>`
Win at rock paper scissors against your opponent to gain your bet
_gains: x1_

**Roulette**
`!roulette <amount>`
Survive to the roulette game to gain your bet. A 6 bullets :gun: is used, the more you replay, the more you gain (x4 if you survive the 5 shots). Answer `continue` to continue using the same :gun: and increase your gain... at your own risks
_gains: from x1 to x4 depending on the round you reach_

[31-May-21 09:35 PM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Economy Plugin
`!buy [name]`
Buy any item from the shop

`!daily`
Claim your daily coins. Claim on consecutive days to earn a streak bonus.

`!coins (optional member)`
Get the coins amount of anyone in the server

`!dice [amount]`
Throw two dice and try to get more points than your opponent to gain coins

`!economy-info`
Everything you need to know about the economy of this server

`!games`
Get more info about server's games

`!give-item [member] [name] [amount]`
Give an item from your inventory to a member

`!guess [amount]`
Guess the number between 1 and 100 to gain coins

`!items (optional member)`
List the items you bought from the shop

`!richest`
Get the richest players of the server

`!rps [amount] [sign]`
Play rock paper scissors and try to gain coins

`!roulette [amount]`
Play roulette and try to gain coins

`!shop (optional name)`
List items from the shop

`!use [name]`
Use an item from your inventory

`!work (optional action)`
Work for one hour and come back to claim your paycheck

[31-May-21 11:55 PM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Economy Plugin
`!buy [name]`
Buy any item from the shop

`!daily`
Claim your daily coins. Claim on consecutive days to earn a streak bonus.

`!coins (optional member)`
Get the coins amount of anyone in the server

`!dice [amount]`
Throw two dice and try to get more points than your opponent to gain coins

`!economy-info`
Everything you need to know about the economy of this server

`!games`
Get more info about server's games

`!give-coins [member] [amount]`
Give coins to anyone in the server

`!give-item [member] [name] [amount]`
Give an item from your inventory to a member

`!guess [amount]`
Guess the number between 1 and 100 to gain coins

`!items (optional member)`
List the items you bought from the shop

`!remove-coins [member] [amount]`
Remove coins from anyone in the server

`!remove-item [member] [name] [amount]`
Remove an item from someone's inventory

`!richest`
Get the richest players of the server

`!rps [amount] [sign]`
Play rock paper scissors and try to gain coins

`!roulette [amount]`
Play roulette and try to gain coins
Page 1/2

[01-Jun-21 10:40 AM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Gamble up to 240 :existentialdread: for each game

**Dice**
`!dice <amount>`
Throw two dice and try to make more than your opponent to gain your bet. Make a double and win twice this amount. Make a double 6 and win three times this amount.
_gains: from x1 to x3 depending on your dice_

**Guess The Number**
`!guess <amount>`
Guess the random number between **1 and 100**, in 5 attempts to gain your bet. The less attempts you use, the more you gain (**x10** in one shot).
_gains: from x0.5 to x10 depending on the attempts_

**Roshambo (rock, paper, scissors)**
`!rps <amount> <sign>`
Win at rock paper scissors against your opponent to gain your bet
_gains: x1_

**Roulette**
`!roulette <amount>`
Survive to the roulette game to gain your bet. A 6 bullets :gun: is used, the more you replay, the more you gain (x4 if you survive the 5 shots). Answer `continue` to continue using the same :gun: and increase your gain... at your own risks
_gains: from x1 to x4 depending on the round you reach_

{Embed}
Economy Plugin
`!buy [name]`
Buy any item from the shop

`!daily`
Claim your daily coins. Claim on consecutive days to earn a streak bonus.

`!coins (optional member)`
Get the coins amount of anyone in the server

`!dice [amount]`
Throw two dice and try to get more points than your opponent to gain coins

`!economy-info`
Everything you need to know about the economy of this server

`!games`
Get more info about server's games

`!give-coins [member] [amount]`
Give coins to anyone in the server

`!give-item [member] [name] [amount]`
Give an item from your inventory to a member

`!guess [amount]`
Guess the number between 1 and 100 to gain coins

`!items (optional member)`
List the items you bought from the shop

`!remove-coins [member] [amount]`
Remove coins from anyone in the server

`!remove-item [member] [name] [amount]`
Remove an item from someone's inventory

`!richest`
Get the richest players of the server

`!rps [amount] [sign]`
Play rock paper scissors and try to gain coins

`!roulette [amount]`
Play roulette and try to gain coins

[01-Jun-21 07:38 PM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Gamble up to 240 :existentialdread: for each game

**Dice**
`!dice <amount>`
Throw two dice and try to make more than your opponent to gain your bet. Make a double and win twice this amount. Make a double 6 and win three times this amount.
_gains: from x1 to x3 depending on your dice_

**Guess The Number**
`!guess <amount>`
Guess the random number between **1 and 100**, in 5 attempts to gain your bet. The less attempts you use, the more you gain (**x10** in one shot).
_gains: from x0.5 to x10 depending on the attempts_

**Roshambo (rock, paper, scissors)**
`!rps <amount> <sign>`
Win at rock paper scissors against your opponent to gain your bet
_gains: x1_

**Roulette**
`!roulette <amount>`
Survive to the roulette game to gain your bet. A 6 bullets :gun: is used, the more you replay, the more you gain (x4 if you survive the 5 shots). Answer `continue` to continue using the same :gun: and increase your gain... at your own risks
_gains: from x1 to x4 depending on the round you reach_

[01-Jun-21 07:51 PM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Gamble up to 240 :existentialdread: for each game

**Dice**
`!dice <amount>`
Throw two dice and try to make more than your opponent to gain your bet. Make a double and win twice this amount. Make a double 6 and win three times this amount.
_gains: from x1 to x3 depending on your dice_

**Guess The Number**
`!guess <amount>`
Guess the random number between **1 and 100**, in 5 attempts to gain your bet. The less attempts you use, the more you gain (**x10** in one shot).
_gains: from x0.5 to x10 depending on the attempts_

**Roshambo (rock, paper, scissors)**
`!rps <amount> <sign>`
Win at rock paper scissors against your opponent to gain your bet
_gains: x1_

**Roulette**
`!roulette <amount>`
Survive to the roulette game to gain your bet. A 6 bullets :gun: is used, the more you replay, the more you gain (x4 if you survive the 5 shots). Answer `continue` to continue using the same :gun: and increase your gain... at your own risks
_gains: from x1 to x4 depending on the round you reach_

{Embed}
Economy Plugin
`!buy [name]`
Buy any item from the shop

`!daily`
Claim your daily coins. Claim on consecutive days to earn a streak bonus.

`!coins (optional member)`
Get the coins amount of anyone in the server

`!dice [amount]`
Throw two dice and try to get more points than your opponent to gain coins

`!economy-info`
Everything you need to know about the economy of this server

`!games`
Get more info about server's games

`!give-coins [member] [amount]`
Give coins to anyone in the server

`!give-item [member] [name] [amount]`
Give an item from your inventory to a member

`!guess [amount]`
Guess the number between 1 and 100 to gain coins

`!items (optional member)`
List the items you bought from the shop

`!remove-coins [member] [amount]`
Remove coins from anyone in the server

`!remove-item [member] [name] [amount]`
Remove an item from someone's inventory

`!richest`
Get the richest players of the server

`!rps [amount] [sign]`
Play rock paper scissors and try to gain coins

`!roulette [amount]`
Play roulette and try to gain coins

[01-Jun-21 08:25 PM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Moderator Plugin
`!ban [member] (optional reason)`
Bans a member from the server

`!tempban [member] [duration] (optional reason)`
Temporarily bans a member from the server

`!clear (optional amount) (optional member)`
Clears messages in a particular channel

`!clear-all-infractions (optional member)`
Remove all the infractions of everyone in the server

`!infractions [member]`
Displays how many infractions this member has

`!kick [member] (optional reason)`
Kicks a member from the server

`!mute [member] (optional reason)`
Mutes a member in the whole server

`!tempmute [member] [duration] (optional reason)`
Temporarily mutes a member in the server

`!role-info [role]`
Gets information about a role

`!server-info`
Gets information about your server

`!slowmode (optional timeout) (optional off)`
Enables/Disables slowmode in a channel

`!unban [member]`
Unbans a member

`!unmute [member]`
Unmutes a member

`!user-info (optional member)`
Gets information about a user

`!warn [member] (optional reason)`
Warns a member
https://i.imgur.com/JsgxK3Y.png

[01-Jun-21 08:44 PM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Economy Plugin
`!buy [name]`
Buy any item from the shop

`!daily`
Claim your daily coins. Claim on consecutive days to earn a streak bonus.

`!coins (optional member)`
Get the coins amount of anyone in the server

`!dice [amount]`
Throw two dice and try to get more points than your opponent to gain coins

`!economy-info`
Everything you need to know about the economy of this server

`!games`
Get more info about server's games

`!give-item [member] [name] [amount]`
Give an item from your inventory to a member

`!guess [amount]`
Guess the number between 1 and 100 to gain coins

`!items (optional member)`
List the items you bought from the shop

`!richest`
Get the richest players of the server

`!rps [amount] [sign]`
Play rock paper scissors and try to gain coins

`!roulette [amount]`
Play roulette and try to gain coins

`!shop (optional name)`
List items from the shop

`!use [name]`
Use an item from your inventory

`!work (optional action)`
Work for one hour and come back to claim your paycheck


[01-Jun-21 08:45 PM] Cefqrn#3081
!games


[01-Jun-21 08:45 PM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Gamble up to 240 :existentialdread: for each game

**Dice**
`!dice <amount>`
Throw two dice and try to make more than your opponent to gain your bet. Make a double and win twice this amount. Make a double 6 and win three times this amount.
_gains: from x1 to x3 depending on your dice_

**Guess The Number**
`!guess <amount>`
Guess the random number between **1 and 100**, in 5 attempts to gain your bet. The less attempts you use, the more you gain (**x10** in one shot).
_gains: from x0.5 to x10 depending on the attempts_

**Roshambo (rock, paper, scissors)**
`!rps <amount> <sign>`
Win at rock paper scissors against your opponent to gain your bet
_gains: x1_

**Roulette**
`!roulette <amount>`
Survive to the roulette game to gain your bet. A 6 bullets :gun: is used, the more you replay, the more you gain (x4 if you survive the 5 shots). Answer `continue` to continue using the same :gun: and increase your gain... at your own risks
_gains: from x1 to x4 depending on the round you reach_

[03-Jun-21 01:11 AM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Economy Plugin
`!buy [name]`
Buy any item from the shop

`!daily`
Claim your daily coins. Claim on consecutive days to earn a streak bonus.

`!coins (optional member)`
Get the coins amount of anyone in the server

`!dice [amount]`
Throw two dice and try to get more points than your opponent to gain coins

`!economy-info`
Everything you need to know about the economy of this server

`!games`
Get more info about server's games

`!give-coins [member] [amount]`
Give coins to anyone in the server

`!give-item [member] [name] [amount]`
Give an item from your inventory to a member

`!guess [amount]`
Guess the number between 1 and 100 to gain coins

`!items (optional member)`
List the items you bought from the shop

`!remove-coins [member] [amount]`
Remove coins from anyone in the server

`!remove-item [member] [name] [amount]`
Remove an item from someone's inventory

`!richest`
Get the richest players of the server

`!rps [amount] [sign]`
Play rock paper scissors and try to gain coins

`!roulette [amount]`
Play roulette and try to gain coins

[03-Jun-21 01:11 AM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Gamble up to 240 :existentialdread: for each game

**Dice**
`!dice <amount>`
Throw two dice and try to make more than your opponent to gain your bet. Make a double and win twice this amount. Make a double 6 and win three times this amount.
_gains: from x1 to x3 depending on your dice_

**Guess The Number**
`!guess <amount>`
Guess the random number between **1 and 100**, in 5 attempts to gain your bet. The less attempts you use, the more you gain (**x10** in one shot).
_gains: from x0.5 to x10 depending on the attempts_

**Roshambo (rock, paper, scissors)**
`!rps <amount> <sign>`
Win at rock paper scissors against your opponent to gain your bet
_gains: x1_

**Roulette**
`!roulette <amount>`
Survive to the roulette game to gain your bet. A 6 bullets :gun: is used, the more you replay, the more you gain (x4 if you survive the 5 shots). Answer `continue` to continue using the same :gun: and increase your gain... at your own risks
_gains: from x1 to x4 depending on the round you reach_

[03-Jun-21 01:13 AM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Economy Plugin
`!buy [name]`
Buy any item from the shop

`!daily`
Claim your daily coins. Claim on consecutive days to earn a streak bonus.

`!coins (optional member)`
Get the coins amount of anyone in the server

`!dice [amount]`
Throw two dice and try to get more points than your opponent to gain coins

`!economy-info`
Everything you need to know about the economy of this server

`!games`
Get more info about server's games

`!give-item [member] [name] [amount]`
Give an item from your inventory to a member

`!guess [amount]`
Guess the number between 1 and 100 to gain coins

`!items (optional member)`
List the items you bought from the shop

`!richest`
Get the richest players of the server

`!rps [amount] [sign]`
Play rock paper scissors and try to gain coins

`!roulette [amount]`
Play roulette and try to gain coins

`!shop (optional name)`
List items from the shop

`!use [name]`
Use an item from your inventory

`!work (optional action)`
Work for one hour and come back to claim your paycheck

[03-Jun-21 07:02 PM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Economy Plugin
`!buy [name]`
Buy any item from the shop

`!daily`
Claim your daily coins. Claim on consecutive days to earn a streak bonus.

`!coins (optional member)`
Get the coins amount of anyone in the server

`!dice [amount]`
Throw two dice and try to get more points than your opponent to gain coins

`!economy-info`
Everything you need to know about the economy of this server

`!games`
Get more info about server's games

`!give-item [member] [name] [amount]`
Give an item from your inventory to a member

`!guess [amount]`
Guess the number between 1 and 100 to gain coins

`!items (optional member)`
List the items you bought from the shop

`!richest`
Get the richest players of the server

`!rps [amount] [sign]`
Play rock paper scissors and try to gain coins

`!roulette [amount]`
Play roulette and try to gain coins

`!shop (optional name)`
List items from the shop

`!use [name]`
Use an item from your inventory

`!work (optional action)`
Work for one hour and come back to claim your paycheck

Hopson Community Server Economy
:dollar: Currency
MEE6 coins :existentialdread:
:moneybag: Daily claim
You can claim **once a day** using the command `!daily` and the reward can vary from **50** :existentialdread: to **120** :existentialdread:.
Claim on consecutive days to earn a streak bonus (**x4** for **7 days** in a **row**).
:slot_machine: Gamble
You can gamble up to **240** :existentialdread: for each game.

[04-Jun-21 03:21 PM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Economy Plugin
`!buy [name]`
Buy any item from the shop

`!daily`
Claim your daily coins. Claim on consecutive days to earn a streak bonus.

`!coins (optional member)`
Get the coins amount of anyone in the server

`!dice [amount]`
Throw two dice and try to get more points than your opponent to gain coins

`!economy-info`
Everything you need to know about the economy of this server

`!games`
Get more info about server's games

`!give-item [member] [name] [amount]`
Give an item from your inventory to a member

`!guess [amount]`
Guess the number between 1 and 100 to gain coins

`!items (optional member)`
List the items you bought from the shop

`!richest`
Get the richest players of the server

`!rps [amount] [sign]`
Play rock paper scissors and try to gain coins

`!roulette [amount]`
Play roulette and try to gain coins

`!shop (optional name)`
List items from the shop

`!use [name]`
Use an item from your inventory

`!work (optional action)`
Work for one hour and come back to claim your paycheck

{Embed}
Economy Plugin
`!buy [name]`
Buy any item from the shop

`!daily`
Claim your daily coins. Claim on consecutive days to earn a streak bonus.

`!coins (optional member)`
Get the coins amount of anyone in the server

`!dice [amount]`
Throw two dice and try to get more points than your opponent to gain coins

`!economy-info`
Everything you need to know about the economy of this server

`!games`
Get more info about server's games

`!give-item [member] [name] [amount]`
Give an item from your inventory to a member

`!guess [amount]`
Guess the number between 1 and 100 to gain coins

`!items (optional member)`
List the items you bought from the shop

`!richest`
Get the richest players of the server

`!rps [amount] [sign]`
Play rock paper scissors and try to gain coins

`!roulette [amount]`
Play roulette and try to gain coins

`!shop (optional name)`
List items from the shop

`!use [name]`
Use an item from your inventory

`!work (optional action)`
Work for one hour and come back to claim your paycheck

[04-Jun-21 08:26 PM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Economy Plugin
`!buy [name]`
Buy any item from the shop

`!daily`
Claim your daily coins. Claim on consecutive days to earn a streak bonus.

`!coins (optional member)`
Get the coins amount of anyone in the server

`!dice [amount]`
Throw two dice and try to get more points than your opponent to gain coins

`!economy-info`
Everything you need to know about the economy of this server

`!games`
Get more info about server's games

`!give-item [member] [name] [amount]`
Give an item from your inventory to a member

`!guess [amount]`
Guess the number between 1 and 100 to gain coins

`!items (optional member)`
List the items you bought from the shop

`!richest`
Get the richest players of the server

`!rps [amount] [sign]`
Play rock paper scissors and try to gain coins

`!roulette [amount]`
Play roulette and try to gain coins

`!shop (optional name)`
List items from the shop

`!use [name]`
Use an item from your inventory

`!work (optional action)`
Work for one hour and come back to claim your paycheck

[05-Jun-21 07:11 PM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Economy Plugin
`!buy [name]`
Buy any item from the shop

`!daily`
Claim your daily coins. Claim on consecutive days to earn a streak bonus.

`!coins (optional member)`
Get the coins amount of anyone in the server

`!dice [amount]`
Throw two dice and try to get more points than your opponent to gain coins

`!economy-info`
Everything you need to know about the economy of this server

`!games`
Get more info about server's games

`!give-item [member] [name] [amount]`
Give an item from your inventory to a member

`!guess [amount]`
Guess the number between 1 and 100 to gain coins

`!items (optional member)`
List the items you bought from the shop

`!richest`
Get the richest players of the server

`!rps [amount] [sign]`
Play rock paper scissors and try to gain coins

`!roulette [amount]`
Play roulette and try to gain coins

`!shop (optional name)`
List items from the shop

`!use [name]`
Use an item from your inventory

`!work (optional action)`
Work for one hour and come back to claim your paycheck

[05-Jun-21 07:11 PM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Gamble up to 240 :existentialdread: for each game

**Dice**
`!dice <amount>`
Throw two dice and try to make more than your opponent to gain your bet. Make a double and win twice this amount. Make a double 6 and win three times this amount.
_gains: from x1 to x3 depending on your dice_

**Guess The Number**
`!guess <amount>`
Guess the random number between **1 and 100**, in 5 attempts to gain your bet. The less attempts you use, the more you gain (**x10** in one shot).
_gains: from x0.5 to x10 depending on the attempts_

**Roshambo (rock, paper, scissors)**
`!rps <amount> <sign>`
Win at rock paper scissors against your opponent to gain your bet
_gains: x1_

**Roulette**
`!roulette <amount>`
Survive to the roulette game to gain your bet. A 6 bullets :gun: is used, the more you replay, the more you gain (x4 if you survive the 5 shots). Answer `continue` to continue using the same :gun: and increase your gain... at your own risks
_gains: from x1 to x4 depending on the round you reach_

[05-Jun-21 07:18 PM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Gamble up to 240 :existentialdread: for each game

**Dice**
`!dice <amount>`
Throw two dice and try to make more than your opponent to gain your bet. Make a double and win twice this amount. Make a double 6 and win three times this amount.
_gains: from x1 to x3 depending on your dice_

**Guess The Number**
`!guess <amount>`
Guess the random number between **1 and 100**, in 5 attempts to gain your bet. The less attempts you use, the more you gain (**x10** in one shot).
_gains: from x0.5 to x10 depending on the attempts_

**Roshambo (rock, paper, scissors)**
`!rps <amount> <sign>`
Win at rock paper scissors against your opponent to gain your bet
_gains: x1_

**Roulette**
`!roulette <amount>`
Survive to the roulette game to gain your bet. A 6 bullets :gun: is used, the more you replay, the more you gain (x4 if you survive the 5 shots). Answer `continue` to continue using the same :gun: and increase your gain... at your own risks
_gains: from x1 to x4 depending on the round you reach_

[05-Jun-21 07:28 PM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Economy Plugin
`!buy [name]`
Buy any item from the shop

`!daily`
Claim your daily coins. Claim on consecutive days to earn a streak bonus.

`!coins (optional member)`
Get the coins amount of anyone in the server

`!dice [amount]`
Throw two dice and try to get more points than your opponent to gain coins

`!economy-info`
Everything you need to know about the economy of this server

`!games`
Get more info about server's games

`!give-item [member] [name] [amount]`
Give an item from your inventory to a member

`!guess [amount]`
Guess the number between 1 and 100 to gain coins

`!items (optional member)`
List the items you bought from the shop

`!richest`
Get the richest players of the server

`!rps [amount] [sign]`
Play rock paper scissors and try to gain coins

`!roulette [amount]`
Play roulette and try to gain coins

`!shop (optional name)`
List items from the shop

`!use [name]`
Use an item from your inventory

`!work (optional action)`
Work for one hour and come back to claim your paycheck

[05-Jun-21 07:31 PM] Binkiklou#7592
!games


[05-Jun-21 07:31 PM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Gamble up to 240 :existentialdread: for each game

**Dice**
`!dice <amount>`
Throw two dice and try to make more than your opponent to gain your bet. Make a double and win twice this amount. Make a double 6 and win three times this amount.
_gains: from x1 to x3 depending on your dice_

**Guess The Number**
`!guess <amount>`
Guess the random number between **1 and 100**, in 5 attempts to gain your bet. The less attempts you use, the more you gain (**x10** in one shot).
_gains: from x0.5 to x10 depending on the attempts_

**Roshambo (rock, paper, scissors)**
`!rps <amount> <sign>`
Win at rock paper scissors against your opponent to gain your bet
_gains: x1_

**Roulette**
`!roulette <amount>`
Survive to the roulette game to gain your bet. A 6 bullets :gun: is used, the more you replay, the more you gain (x4 if you survive the 5 shots). Answer `continue` to continue using the same :gun: and increase your gain... at your own risks
_gains: from x1 to x4 depending on the round you reach_

[05-Jun-21 07:34 PM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Gamble up to 240 :existentialdread: for each game

**Dice**
`!dice <amount>`
Throw two dice and try to make more than your opponent to gain your bet. Make a double and win twice this amount. Make a double 6 and win three times this amount.
_gains: from x1 to x3 depending on your dice_

**Guess The Number**
`!guess <amount>`
Guess the random number between **1 and 100**, in 5 attempts to gain your bet. The less attempts you use, the more you gain (**x10** in one shot).
_gains: from x0.5 to x10 depending on the attempts_

**Roshambo (rock, paper, scissors)**
`!rps <amount> <sign>`
Win at rock paper scissors against your opponent to gain your bet
_gains: x1_

**Roulette**
`!roulette <amount>`
Survive to the roulette game to gain your bet. A 6 bullets :gun: is used, the more you replay, the more you gain (x4 if you survive the 5 shots). Answer `continue` to continue using the same :gun: and increase your gain... at your own risks
_gains: from x1 to x4 depending on the round you reach_

{Embed}
Gamble up to 240 :existentialdread: for each game

**Dice**
`!dice <amount>`
Throw two dice and try to make more than your opponent to gain your bet. Make a double and win twice this amount. Make a double 6 and win three times this amount.
_gains: from x1 to x3 depending on your dice_

**Guess The Number**
`!guess <amount>`
Guess the random number between **1 and 100**, in 5 attempts to gain your bet. The less attempts you use, the more you gain (**x10** in one shot).
_gains: from x0.5 to x10 depending on the attempts_

**Roshambo (rock, paper, scissors)**
`!rps <amount> <sign>`
Win at rock paper scissors against your opponent to gain your bet
_gains: x1_

**Roulette**
`!roulette <amount>`
Survive to the roulette game to gain your bet. A 6 bullets :gun: is used, the more you replay, the more you gain (x4 if you survive the 5 shots). Answer `continue` to continue using the same :gun: and increase your gain... at your own risks
_gains: from x1 to x4 depending on the round you reach_

;compile lua
```

coins = 0
   for i=1,100000 do
      r1 = math.random(1,6)
      r2 = math.random(1,6)
      or1 = math.random(1,6)
      or2 = math.random(1,6)
      if r1 + r2 == 12 then
        coins = coins + 720 
      elseif r1 + r2 > or1 + or2 then
         if r1 == r2 then
            coins = coins + 480
         else
            coins = coins + 240
         end
      elseif r1 + r2 < or1 + or2 then
         coins = coins - 240
      end
   end
   print(coins/100000)
```

[06-Jun-21 01:00 AM] The Emerald Derp Leader#4510
;compile lua
```
coins = 0
   for guts=1,5 do
      for i=1,1000000 do
         won = true
         for i=1,guts do
            if math.random(1,7-i) == 1 then
               won = false
            end
         end
         if won then
            if guts == 1 then
               coins = coins+24
            elseif guts == 2 then
               coins = coins+72
            elseif guts == 3 then
               coins = coins+192
            elseif guts == 4 then
               coins = coins+360
            elseif guts == 5 then
               coins = coins+720
            end
         else
            coins = coins - 240
         end
      end
      print("guts "..guts..": "..(coins/1000000))
   end

```

[06-Jun-21 04:30 PM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Economy Plugin
`!buy [name]`
Buy any item from the shop

`!daily`
Claim your daily coins. Claim on consecutive days to earn a streak bonus.

`!coins (optional member)`
Get the coins amount of anyone in the server

`!dice [amount]`
Throw two dice and try to get more points than your opponent to gain coins

`!economy-info`
Everything you need to know about the economy of this server

`!games`
Get more info about server's games

`!give-item [member] [name] [amount]`
Give an item from your inventory to a member

`!guess [amount]`
Guess the number between 1 and 100 to gain coins

`!items (optional member)`
List the items you bought from the shop

`!richest`
Get the richest players of the server

`!rps [amount] [sign]`
Play rock paper scissors and try to gain coins

`!roulette [amount]`
Play roulette and try to gain coins

`!shop (optional name)`
List items from the shop

`!use [name]`
Use an item from your inventory

`!work (optional action)`
Work for one hour and come back to claim your paycheck

[06-Jun-21 04:32 PM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Gamble up to 240 :existentialdread: for each game

**Dice**
`!dice <amount>`
Throw two dice and try to make more than your opponent to gain your bet. Make a double and win twice this amount. Make a double 6 and win three times this amount.
_gains: from x1 to x3 depending on your dice_

**Guess The Number**
`!guess <amount>`
Guess the random number between **1 and 100**, in 5 attempts to gain your bet. The less attempts you use, the more you gain (**x10** in one shot).
_gains: from x0.5 to x10 depending on the attempts_

**Roshambo (rock, paper, scissors)**
`!rps <amount> <sign>`
Win at rock paper scissors against your opponent to gain your bet
_gains: x1_

**Roulette**
`!roulette <amount>`
Survive to the roulette game to gain your bet. A 6 bullets :gun: is used, the more you replay, the more you gain (x4 if you survive the 5 shots). Answer `continue` to continue using the same :gun: and increase your gain... at your own risks
_gains: from x1 to x4 depending on the round you reach_

[06-Jun-21 05:28 PM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Economy Plugin
`!buy [name]`
Buy any item from the shop

`!daily`
Claim your daily coins. Claim on consecutive days to earn a streak bonus.

`!coins (optional member)`
Get the coins amount of anyone in the server

`!dice [amount]`
Throw two dice and try to get more points than your opponent to gain coins

`!economy-info`
Everything you need to know about the economy of this server

`!games`
Get more info about server's games

`!give-item [member] [name] [amount]`
Give an item from your inventory to a member

`!guess [amount]`
Guess the number between 1 and 100 to gain coins

`!items (optional member)`
List the items you bought from the shop

`!richest`
Get the richest players of the server

`!rps [amount] [sign]`
Play rock paper scissors and try to gain coins

`!roulette [amount]`
Play roulette and try to gain coins

`!shop (optional name)`
List items from the shop

`!use [name]`
Use an item from your inventory

`!work (optional action)`
Work for one hour and come back to claim your paycheck

[06-Jun-21 07:39 PM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Economy Plugin
`!buy [name]`
Buy any item from the shop

`!daily`
Claim your daily coins. Claim on consecutive days to earn a streak bonus.

`!coins (optional member)`
Get the coins amount of anyone in the server

`!dice [amount]`
Throw two dice and try to get more points than your opponent to gain coins

`!economy-info`
Everything you need to know about the economy of this server

`!games`
Get more info about server's games

`!give-item [member] [name] [amount]`
Give an item from your inventory to a member

`!guess [amount]`
Guess the number between 1 and 100 to gain coins

`!items (optional member)`
List the items you bought from the shop

`!richest`
Get the richest players of the server

`!rps [amount] [sign]`
Play rock paper scissors and try to gain coins

`!roulette [amount]`
Play roulette and try to gain coins

`!shop (optional name)`
List items from the shop

`!use [name]`
Use an item from your inventory

`!work (optional action)`
Work for one hour and come back to claim your paycheck

[08-Jun-21 11:22 PM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Economy Plugin
`!buy [name]`
Buy any item from the shop

`!daily`
Claim your daily coins. Claim on consecutive days to earn a streak bonus.

`!coins (optional member)`
Get the coins amount of anyone in the server

`!dice [amount]`
Throw two dice and try to get more points than your opponent to gain coins

`!economy-info`
Everything you need to know about the economy of this server

`!games`
Get more info about server's games

`!give-item [member] [name] [amount]`
Give an item from your inventory to a member

`!guess [amount]`
Guess the number between 1 and 100 to gain coins

`!items (optional member)`
List the items you bought from the shop

`!richest`
Get the richest players of the server

`!rps [amount] [sign]`
Play rock paper scissors and try to gain coins

`!roulette [amount]`
Play roulette and try to gain coins

`!shop (optional name)`
List items from the shop

`!use [name]`
Use an item from your inventory

`!work (optional action)`
Work for one hour and come back to claim your paycheck

[11-Jun-21 02:07 PM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Economy Plugin
`!buy [name]`
Buy any item from the shop

`!daily`
Claim your daily coins. Claim on consecutive days to earn a streak bonus.

`!coins (optional member)`
Get the coins amount of anyone in the server

`!dice [amount]`
Throw two dice and try to get more points than your opponent to gain coins

`!economy-info`
Everything you need to know about the economy of this server

`!games`
Get more info about server's games

`!give-item [member] [name] [amount]`
Give an item from your inventory to a member

`!guess [amount]`
Guess the number between 1 and 100 to gain coins

`!items (optional member)`
List the items you bought from the shop

`!richest`
Get the richest players of the server

`!rps [amount] [sign]`
Play rock paper scissors and try to gain coins

`!roulette [amount]`
Play roulette and try to gain coins

`!shop (optional name)`
List items from the shop

`!use [name]`
Use an item from your inventory

`!work (optional action)`
Work for one hour and come back to claim your paycheck

[11-Jun-21 02:07 PM] oboforty#5439
!games


[11-Jun-21 02:07 PM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Gamble up to 240 :existentialdread: for each game

**Dice**
`!dice <amount>`
Throw two dice and try to make more than your opponent to gain your bet. Make a double and win twice this amount. Make a double 6 and win three times this amount.
_gains: from x1 to x3 depending on your dice_

**Guess The Number**
`!guess <amount>`
Guess the random number between **1 and 100**, in 5 attempts to gain your bet. The less attempts you use, the more you gain (**x10** in one shot).
_gains: from x0.5 to x10 depending on the attempts_

**Roshambo (rock, paper, scissors)**
`!rps <amount> <sign>`
Win at rock paper scissors against your opponent to gain your bet
_gains: x1_

**Roulette**
`!roulette <amount>`
Survive to the roulette game to gain your bet. A 6 bullets :gun: is used, the more you replay, the more you gain (x4 if you survive the 5 shots). Answer `continue` to continue using the same :gun: and increase your gain... at your own risks
_gains: from x1 to x4 depending on the round you reach_

[11-Jun-21 06:02 PM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Economy Plugin
`!buy [name]`
Buy any item from the shop

`!daily`
Claim your daily coins. Claim on consecutive days to earn a streak bonus.

`!coins (optional member)`
Get the coins amount of anyone in the server

`!dice [amount]`
Throw two dice and try to get more points than your opponent to gain coins

`!economy-info`
Everything you need to know about the economy of this server

`!games`
Get more info about server's games

`!give-item [member] [name] [amount]`
Give an item from your inventory to a member

`!guess [amount]`
Guess the number between 1 and 100 to gain coins

`!items (optional member)`
List the items you bought from the shop

`!richest`
Get the richest players of the server

`!rps [amount] [sign]`
Play rock paper scissors and try to gain coins

`!roulette [amount]`
Play roulette and try to gain coins

`!shop (optional name)`
List items from the shop

`!use [name]`
Use an item from your inventory

`!work (optional action)`
Work for one hour and come back to claim your paycheck

[11-Jun-21 10:51 PM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Economy Plugin
`/buy [name]`
Buy any item from the shop

`/daily`
Claim your daily coins. Claim on consecutive days to earn a streak bonus.

`/coins (optional member)`
Get the coins amount of anyone in the server

`/dice [amount]`
Throw two dice and try to get more points than your opponent to gain coins

`/economy-info`
Everything you need to know about the economy of this server

`/games`
Get more info about server's games

`/give-item [member] [name] [amount]`
Give an item from your inventory to a member

`/guess [amount]`
Guess the number between 1 and 100 to gain coins

`/items (optional member)`
List the items you bought from the shop

`/richest`
Get the richest players of the server

`/rps [amount] [sign]`
Play rock paper scissors and try to gain coins

`/roulette [amount]`
Play roulette and try to gain coins

`/shop (optional name)`
List items from the shop

`/use [name]`
Use an item from your inventory

`/work (optional action)`
Work for one hour and come back to claim your paycheck

{Embed}
https://stackoverflow.com/questions/388242/the-definitive-c-book-guide-and-list
The Definitive C++ Book Guide and List
This question attempts to collect the few pearls among the dozens of bad C++ books that are published every year.
Unlike many other programming languages, which are often picked up on the go from
https://cdn.sstatic.net/Sites/stackoverflow/Img/apple-touch-icon@2.png?v=73d79a89bded

[11-Jun-21 11:10 PM] MEE6#4876

{Embed}
Economy Plugin
`/buy [name]`
Buy any item from the shop

`/daily`
Claim your daily coins. Claim on consecutive days to earn a streak bonus.

`/coins (optional member)`
Get the coins amount of anyone in the server

`/dice [amount]`
Throw two dice and try to get more points than your opponent to gain coins

`/economy-info`
Everything you need to know about the economy of this server

`/games`
Get more info about server's games

`/give-item [member] [name] [amount]`
Give an item from your inventory to a member

`/guess [amount]`
Guess the number between 1 and 100 to gain coins

`/items (optional member)`
List the items you bought from the shop

`/richest`
Get the richest players of the server

`/rps [amount] [sign]`
Play rock paper scissors and try to gain coins

`/roulette [amount]`
Play roulette and try to gain coins

`/shop (optional name)`
List items from the shop

`/use [name]`
Use an item from your inventory

`/work (optional action)`
Work for one hour and come back to claim your paycheck
